snippet.title: A North Carolina man just won a $750,000 lawsuit after suing his wife's lover
snippet.description:
A North Carolina man just won a $750,000 lawsuit after suing his wife's lover 
According to court documents, Kevin Howard recently won a judgment against his ex-wife's lover for "alienation of affections" -- a claim that exists in just a handful of other states across the countr... 
https://news.google.com/articles/CAIiEDG4LzVFAo84sUlsKMKRBiYqGQgEKhAIACoHCAowocv1CjCSptoCMPrTpgU?hl=en-US&gl=US&ceid=US%3Aen
